      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/8446b484-7663-11e4-ad19-5254006e85c2).  Ran 7 tests.  3 tests failed: conf-sanity, sanityn, sanity.",
